    <briefdescription>
<para>The <ref refid="classDali_1_1PixelData" kindref="compound">PixelData</ref> object holds a pixel buffer . The <ref refid="classDali_1_1PixelData" kindref="compound">PixelData</ref> takes over the ownership of the pixel buffer. The buffer memory must NOT be released outside of this class, instead, the <ref refid="classDali_1_1PixelData" kindref="compound">PixelData</ref> object will release it automatically when the reference count falls to zero. </para>
    </briefdescription>
